org.bson

Class BsonDbPointer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bson.BsonValue
      • org.bson.BsonDbPointer

  • public class BsonDbPointer
extends BsonValue
    Holder for a BSON type DBPointer(0x0c). It's deprecated in BSON Specification and present here because of compatibility reasons.

    3.0
